{
  "voice_id": "7kXNOCqiaLdszL0OEXks",
  "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
  "voice_settings": {
    "stability": 0.65,
    "similarity_boost": 0.65,
    "style": 0.0,
    "speed": 1.13,
    "use_speaker_boost": true
  },
  "pronunciation_dictionary_locators": [
    {
      "pronunciation_dictionary_id": "AhK3J8mZDRoShxfoJLk6",
      "version_id": "pFvyQBbxEBKyF7C3IHpy"
    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "N P M just got hijacked. Again. Tan Stack just got hijacked in six minutes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4041e68d18bd0242457c6e4ca4bc5492a1ab13c552087ea266f5e0f529b85461",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 4.829750566893424,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "And revoking the stolen token nukes your home folder.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cf0ea4b6e2244dc6415804fbbfffec4a36e1f6b1a4025c160cf26c604d66e8fe",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 15
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Trusted publishing was supposed to stop this.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9e2d600f3c12c1d39fa568db63457df36917300b7b7a0f6d2bf3832874faece9",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 2.461315192743764,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 24
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "But the malware shipped signed. Salsa-attested. Still malware.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8b8a93ba1263978464a4c11a06e05f683b63a7bb2f79463c5741222a2f540d6b",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 3.575873015873016,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 31
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Trusted publishing is not a trust boundary.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e2d1984bdc27f64e6e0e21827c66fab4ca9d6996d3e37eb411d64327ae500cab",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 2.2291156462585033,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 39
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "It is a permissions boundary. Mini shy hu-lood proved it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8c5fef3b918e8ff192ddff5f526382c0758a8a1ce587419b213541fbfc583740",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 46
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "So how did one fork-PR own Tan Stack? Here's the smoking gun.",
      "checksum": "sha256:56d5208ed57bb3c1f55dca728bc330db7333bdf6592cefa0be9fb42f9699968c",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 56
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "A workflow file called bundle-size dot yamel ran on the pull request target trigger.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6c631814d42e5157718091f0272b587dee64817542cd036d1429f5e63eef1195",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 4.73687074829932,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 68
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "That single line means fork code runs with main-repo permissions.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0ffc7b53573fd4cf06caba80f65a1afcb5fdc724483f38194ddc18015a10c416",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 82
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Then it checked out the merge commit of the attacker's PR.",
      "checksum": "sha256:63eb961b88b98d31674cfeda074a66ea27ba700ccb3f42843e9062d11ed11995",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 92
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Fork code. Real secrets. Same runner. The attacker closed the PR moments later.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1acb282aeee0ae957e0f107d5c2c16c2972fae9f50f8ffa38339b0191eb550e6",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 5.294149659863946,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 103
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "The damage was already cached.\n\nAnd here is why closing the PR did nothing.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6ed47450646e74dd6734b2c3c6fb6b62ad6e5b0d551e469f92001e9729cb6073",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 4.272471655328798,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 116
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Github Actions wrote a one-point-one gigabyte poisoned cache to disk.",
      "checksum": "sha256:234c212efe40a7130ee208b1aad3f0a400617d1109dd315eb3ddb6b99e87aca1",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 4.08671201814059,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 130
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "The cache poisons. The fork-PR opens, then closes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9114cf0d50eb8722e8d7b8e77888824edd5cdfba8fcdb01c36057e1a2dc6fa4c",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 3.622312925170068,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 140
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Hours later, an unrelated maintainer merges a real change.",
      "checksum": "sha256:89f4dbffe47901259cb08db88813b5949aa372eb639254ad9452ce23c559e3bb",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 3.3436734693877552,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 148
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "C I pulls the cache. The worm wakes up. It scrapes the O I D C token straight out of slash-proc slash-pid slash-mem.",
      "checksum": "sha256:818235b5fbac8c14fbca3ab0296d1d780c08b22e41ef975894b09aa0d5582cf5",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 6.826666666666667,
      "word_count": 23,
      "words_offset": 157
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Eighty-four Tan Stack versions published before anyone refreshed npmjs dot com.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2359919a306ec95402838214b96a3aeff1566553bc88bb60e03b5771ac8b06fd",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 4.73687074829932,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 180
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "And that is how a Tan Stack problem became everybody's problem.",
      "checksum": "sha256:11ad709ca81ed96101ebc63b69894448387137f2924c1ba6a6bbecd7b8c9e0c0",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 191
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "By the next morning, eye-key-doh tracked three-hundred seventy-three poisoned versions across one-hundred sixty-nine packages.",
      "checksum": "sha256:38ce2ebd1dea1b5053b82983b9818438b2309a0042e879890dc0c311d4d1f330",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 7.430385487528345,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 202
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Five-hundred eighteen million weekly downloads.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2fd092da0e56ab2c93f84a1b5ed57b65036a6178ea33141fb48a67548bc836dd",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 2.693514739229025,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 216
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "Mis-trahl. You-eye-path. Open Search. Guardrails.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3ea12f7b7dfa1f0daf30aaf4a238c494124f16a10d0a60370633017a5dfc56ca",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 3.575873015873016,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 221
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "Squawk. If you ship to N P M, your token was the next link in the chain.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c5439d1823f218b0256e89bc07472a725f7248eeb70b3997fd8f94f8571e9525",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 4.4117913832199545,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 226
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "The worm did not pick targets. It picked maintainers.",
      "checksum": "sha256:68671ce2708bcfd11256dd8faa45a2b9941f4ffe4ecce745402795b8827f1ffd",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 243
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "But the worm did not stop at publishing.",
      "checksum": "sha256:29b1c36fee4b8c8acdd3c6cc90dc9e1d6ff11c3bb8ed977ebf601824f5681262",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 1.9969160997732427,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 252
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "Here is the twist. You run N P M uninstall.",
      "checksum": "sha256:90bcd689b9ea8c2ec35c362121a21839d96debdbfb309e6ca3932f07933a268a",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 260
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "The package leaves. The malware stays. It writes itself into your Claude Code hooks and your V S Code tasks.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d9d4bf8790f1c17404569e74f5a10bd961e6fb181099237f3d5819ea10c11ac5",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 6.455147392290249,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 270
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "Reopen your editor, it runs again. Then it signs forged commits as claude at users dot noreply dot github dot com.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b1806af92cbe4e4e6afaf4cc5f90759e295a60cdef11efebdd26b6171a0a7cd6",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 6.2693877551020405,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 290
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "Branch names from a Dune wordlist. Your AI commits are not a trust signal anymore.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8e5d7f98e1f38113458818986f5d361758be723c4d23ddb097865bc2525ba0ce",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 311
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "And my favorite part. The dead-man switch.",
      "checksum": "sha256:27e94083eb3d84d957ee5b57fcf53cba450fa9fff4550b6d795dd7e123d31b55",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 2.2755555555555556,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 326
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "A daemon polls Github every sixty seconds.",
      "checksum": "sha256:67e777945bfff8b537fa17da3ae76bc39a6a145f484c2abe121af49b4e7d01bb",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 2.507755102040816,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 333
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "If your token throws a forty-X error, it runs r-m dash r-f tilde slash on your machine.",
      "checksum": "sha256:525fcb3a0d49ff964c6b8edf0ac63e21d90f58b424c011b76290d0f2ed676414",
      "wav": "chunk-30.wav",
      "duration": 5.433469387755102,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 340
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "text": "The token name? If you revoke this token, it will wipe the computer of the owner.",
      "checksum": "sha256:212cb3d5c5e161cd15e20efb2cdf5f7de8f8eea8bf8601f297765e983c3e00db",
      "wav": "chunk-31.wav",
      "duration": 4.4117913832199545,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 357
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "text": "That is the literal string. Revoke the token and you delete your home folder.",
      "checksum": "sha256:58f5bf846d144a8641840225f95cf2e4bbadaf146a7c800e517d9595c13ed242",
      "wav": "chunk-32.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 373
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "text": "The cleanup is the trap. So how do you stop this?",
      "checksum": "sha256:75848114be432499b9323f9b4ecdac4d4385d5874146b56a57d88ec6c2d2e7b5",
      "wav": "chunk-33.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 387
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "text": "The fix already shipped. P N P M version eleven defaults block the chain.",
      "checksum": "sha256:be174ed188a68376bf3c6a016e12dd0b73f2b58433b4b403c907dfd104b6620b",
      "wav": "chunk-34.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 398
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "text": "One: minimum release age of twenty-four hours, so new packages sit dormant.",
      "checksum": "sha256:37b280e6a543f98eb2e32fac4d38761be124f1e4cb8f55a45f15cf1a490fe694",
      "wav": "chunk-35.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 412
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "text": "Two: block exotic sub-deps refuses git and tarball deps.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3ed91ecd42dedff1816daf5a3076fb591fab3d5889b4ee5a3f9a4a273d3ba61a",
      "wav": "chunk-36.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 424
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "text": "Three: approved-builds gates every install script behind your confirmation.",
      "checksum": "sha256:09e84a7dc50aa022a301448b6b0e8bf962dca130e8c923f3d6159ee260ec907a",
      "wav": "chunk-37.wav",
      "duration": 4.31891156462585,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 433
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "text": "Three defaults. Already shipped. Almost nobody migrated.\n\nThree P N P M defaults blocked the entire chain.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2a6354242bc8a3b17c05fb81bb78ec5c6d0adeb93ffeb4aa5ec821efd2065707",
      "wav": "chunk-38.wav",
      "duration": 6.594467120181406,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 442
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "text": "Almost nobody migrated. So, switching today, or waiting for the next worm?",
      "checksum": "sha256:c9a837b9f983c7dd57190a8a3414b90c5edb7e4e75ea07eb492768079f6aa321",
      "wav": "chunk-39.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 459
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "text": "Drop your pick below, and subscribe for the next breakdown.",
      "checksum": "sha256:004ec1359457162319ce4f1f6cae0257e5c7850cdc082ab4f3ffd800d9aae21c",
      "wav": "chunk-40.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 471
    }
  ]
}